[###CHANGELOG###]

v0.50.1 (2018-02-14)
- Updated some dependencies
- Updated to .NET 4.7.1
- Fixed SSL error

v0.50 (2016-02-21)
- Homescreen Categories can now be configured (Name, Order, Visibility)
- Restyled Settings Dialog ( + added Autostart option)
- Shows can now also be added via Link
- Various Bugfixes and performance improvements

v0.41 (2015-08-31)
- Images can now be deactivated completely
- Fixed some homescreen bugs (unknown state, negativ season number)

v0.40 (2015-08-31)
- Improved Parser (New Implementation based on Xpath instead of Regex)
- New Homescreen (Hotfix will follow)
- Minor other fixes and performance improvements

v0.31.1 (2015-07-19)
- Hotfix for v0.31 to cope with slow servers.

v0.31 (2015-07-19)
- Improved automatic selection of episodes in Multiselection
- Improved errorhandling of config save/load
- Minor other bugfixes 

v0.30 (2015-06-27)
- Favorizing of Uploads can now be disabled
- Multiselection: Select multiple episodes using CTRL or SHIFT key and download them at once!

v0.20 (2014-12-22)
- Design Change!! Removed Panorama.
- New Information Provider: The Movie DB
- Favorized Uploads are now used and presented first

v0.16 (2014-09-20)
- Episodes can now be marked as "Downloaded" and "Watched"
- Fixed "New-Episode" not showing up when the first episode of a show is released
- Minor other bugfixes and improvements

v0.15.6 (2014-09-10)
- Added Favicon for Hosters (that's only the start of a new feature)
- Fixed "New-Episode" Reset
- Improved Parser (Tbbt, Sherlock, TrueBlood,...)
- Subbed German Episodes are now per default NOT marked as german

v0.15.5 (2014-09-06)
- fixed width of search textbox
- fixed some bugs on "Add show"-screen
- added restart button in settings
- you can now select and add multiple shows
- removed the need of administrator-rights
- reduced maximum threads to 12
- improved multithreading (performance)
- fixed bug, which caused that searching is not possible
  while shows are updating

v0.15.4 (2014-09-04)
- fixed high cpu usage
- maximum threads increased to 25
- added button to add a new show
- clicking enter at show searching adds the first show in the list
- added ability to disable updater
- updater now checks every 30 minutes (because on a server it's always running,
  so checking only at programstart makes no sense)
- background images can now be disabled

v0.15.3 (2014-09-01)
- ability to set the timeout for the notification (or disable it at all)
- new stats system

v0.15.2 (2014-08-20)
- added icons and ability to favorize an upload
- improved updater

v0.15.1 (2014-08-17)
- improved some light-theme colors
- further integration of app updater
- minor bugfixes

v0.15 (2014-08-16)
- More Theme Settings & Updated Metro Version
- Automatic App Updater + Anonymous User Statistics
- New Marking of the New/Updated Episodes on the Episode Screen
- Some other minor stuff and various bugfixes